Football Destination helps fans discover global football trips with fixtures, stadium tips, and affiliate-powered itineraries—all in a terrace-style, mobile-first layout.

## 🚀 How to Run Locally

1. Clone the repo  
   `git clone https://github.com/pierredev/football-destination.git`

2. Open in VS Code and run with **Live Server**  
   _or_ preview via GitHub Pages:  
   `https://pierredev.github.io/football-destination/`

## 📦 Features

- 🌍 Filter by league, country, date, vibe
- ⚽ Club blocks: stadium info, travel ease, matchday culture
- 🎟️ Affiliate links: flights, hotels, tours, tickets
- 🧳 Itinerary cards: curated weekend trips
- 📱 Fast, mobile-first UX

